    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of explanatory note with June 25 Opinion essay about standardized testing in school, which misstated career of author, Albert G Craz; he never taught in New York City (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An explanatory note with the Opinion essay last week, about standardized testing in schools, misstated the career of the author, Albert G. Craz. Though he was a teacher and administrator in Northport and other school districts in New York State for 35 years, he never taught in New York City.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
